## Remote Control session label

This project appears in the phone's Remote Control session picker as:

> **🛠️🌐 - {{REFERENCE_NAME}} Sysadmin**

The label is stored in `./config.json` as `session_label`. To change it, edit that field and restart the session, or run as root on the relay:

```bash
claude-relay rename {{PROJECT_NAME}} "🛠️🌐 - {{REFERENCE_NAME}} Sysadmin"
claude-relay restart {{PROJECT_NAME}}
```

The default template is `🛠️🌐 - <ReferenceName> Sysadmin`.

